Consumer Insights Manager:<br />
Are you curious about human psychology and a student of human behavior? Do you strive to find creative strategies that will improve the online shopper&rsquo;s experience?<br />
Acumen Brands Inc. is seeking an experienced Insights Manager who will be responsible for collecting and analyzing information that will deliver insightful findings about the consumer and the market place. The Insights Manager will help us create a strategic vision that lead to effective online marketing solutions for our brands.<br />
Responsibilities:<br />
&bull; Develop internal understandings of consumers that identify trends and patterns in consumer behaviors<br />
&bull; Discovers the needs and motivations that drive online&nbsp; shopping behavior<br />
&bull; Delivers insight based direction for strategic planning that supports overall business growth<br />
&bull; Develops awareness of industry benchmarking and best practices, new and emerging capabilities and technologies, competitive analysis and marketing trends<br />
&bull; Assists with executing new item/category selling strategies<br />
&bull; Ensures that target customer is represented in our strategy</p>
<p>
Preferred skills &amp; experience:<br />
&bull; 5+ years experience in online/eCommerce shopper insights or category management<br />
&bull; Bachelors degree in Marketing, Psychology, Anthropology or other related field<br />
&bull; Strong understanding of online shopper behavior with advanced knowledge of eCommerce shopper insights tools, practices, and theories<br />
&bull; Must demonstrate cross functional team leadership skills as well as excellent oral and written communication skills<br />
&bull; Positive, team player attitude<br />
&nbsp;</p>
